reviewText: This is a fast paced program consisting mostly of commentary by fathers, wives, Nuns and Priests.  I learned some surprising details about St Joseph.  You will find him to be a worthy role model.  EWTN.com has the program available in both DVD and VHS for $20.00, much less than Amazon's private sellers.
A great movie for all ages.  If you do not yet have a devotion to St. Joseph, this is a great way to get to know him!
